Beauty and the Beast;;92;;94;;G;;An arrogant young prince (Robby Benson) and his castle's servants fall under the spell of a wicked enchantress, who turns him into the hideous Beast until he learns to love and be loved in return. The spirited, headstrong village girl Belle (Paige O'Hara) enters the Beast's castle after he imprisons her father Maurice (Rex Everhart). With the help of his enchanted servants, including the matronly Mrs. Potts (Angela Lansbury), Belle begins to draw the cold-hearted Beast out of his isolation.;;Fantasy,Animation,Kids & family;;Gary Trousdale,Kirk Wise;;1991;;Paige O'Hara,Robby Benson,Richard White,Jerry Orbach,David Ogden Stiers,Angela Lansbury,Bradley Pierce,Rex Everhart,Jesse Corti,Hal Smith,Jo Anne Worley,Mary Kay Bergman,Brian Cummings,Alvin Epstein,Tony Jay;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/beauty_and_the_beast_1991